<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Payment Confirmation for Your Nosh Order</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div
      style="display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; padding-top: 30px;"
    >
      <img
        style="width: 120px; height: 120px; border-radius: 50%; margin-right: 20px;"
        src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dp6ofrbni/image/upload/v1681933499/WhatsApp_Image_2023-04-17_at_7.41.55_PM_eom1cl.jpg"
        alt="Nosh Application Icon"
      />
      <div style="text-align: left;">
        <h1
          style="color: #dd6b20; font-size: 36px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0;"
        >Nosh</h1>
        <p
          style="color: #dd6b20; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0;"
        >The Authentic Food</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p style="font-size: 24px; margin-top: 30px;">Dear {{name}},</p>

    <p style="font-size: 20px;">We are writing to confirm that your payment for
      your recent order on Nosh has been received. Here are the details of your
      order:</p>

    <table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin-top: 20px;">
      <thead style="background-color: #f2f2f2;">
        <tr>
          <th
            style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd; font-size: 20px;"
          >Item</th>
          <th
            style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd; font-size: 20px;"
          >Price</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {{#each orderItems}}
          <tr>
            <td
              style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd; font-size: 18px;"
            >{{name}}</td>
            <td
              style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd; font-size: 18px;"
            >{{price}}</td>
          </tr>
        {{/each}}
      </tbody>
      <tfoot>
        <tr>
          <td
            style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold;"
          >Total:</td>
          <td
            style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold;"
          >{{total}}</td>
        </tr>
      </tfoot>
    </table>

    <p style="font-size: 20px; margin-top: 30px;">Thank you for using our
      platform to order food! Your order will be prepared and delivered to you
      shortly. If you have any questions or concerns about your order, please
      feel free to contact us.</p>

    <p style="font-size: 20px;">We hope you enjoy your meal and we appreciate
      your business.</p>

    <p style="font-size: 20px;">Best regards,</p>
    <p style="font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px;">The Nosh Team</p>
  </body>
</html>